A class should not have more than one reason to change.
meken kiyanne mekai hitanna api xml kiyala class ekak haduma kiyala eke tina functions 
    1update
    2validate 
    3log   etc  kiyala 
api karanna one ewata venawenama class hadaganna eka.update karana class eke validate karanna
tiyenna baha.eka thama wenna one.eka parakata ekai change karanna puluwan.

